description:
Guy #1

Straight. 21 years old. Student.

6'5" tall, 185 pounds.

Loves to play basketball. "Oh yeah, grew up playing it all the time."

Studying Liberal Arts. "I want to become a teacher. Probably Phys Ed."

Says he's very romantic.

"I was raised by my mom, and she taught me well!"

Guy #2

Straight. 20 years old.

6'2" tall, 185 pounds.

Rides dirt bikes. Has a girlfriend.

Squirter!

Guy #3

Straight. 19 years old. Student.

6'1" tall, 170 pounds. Lots of tall guys today!

Furry butt!

Our camera guy was being overly-imaginative on this one. Hope they cleaned the coffee maker really well!!!
title: Auditions 34
